sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant S as Source
  participant F as FinOps_Service
  participant I as Interaction
  participant BA as BillingAccumulator
  participant MP as ModelPricing
  participant CL as CostLedger

  S->>F: evento(tokens, modelo)
  F->>I: insert interaction
  F->>MP: select pricing vigente
  F->>BA: lock balde
  F->>BA: soma tokens

  alt tokens < minimo
    F-->>S: ok sem ledger
  else tokens >= minimo
    loop enquanto >= minimo
      F->>BA: subtrai minimo
      alt manual
        F->>CL: insert ledger manual
      else automacao
        F->>CL: insert ledger rateado
      end
    end
    F->>BA: update acumulador
    F-->>S: ok ledger gerado
  end
